# Delivery — definition of done (agents)

- **Deploy claim:** Say "deployed" / "prod is live" only after **successful Deploy to production** workflow for the target SHA **and** coordinator agent post-deploy smoke per [docs/PROD_SMOKE.md](../../docs/PROD_SMOKE.md). Merge to `master` alone does not deploy.
- **Who verifies:** Coordinator or delegated e2e/browser agent. **Not** the human user unless they are debugging with you.
- **CI E2E:** Green deploy-workflow E2E is the automated agent smoke layer before G3; prod 5-point check still runs after real Firebase deploy.
- **Forbidden:** "Test on prod", "check production yourself", or handing [PROD_SMOKE.md](../../docs/PROD_SMOKE.md) to the user as a task list.
